Specifically, the playbook line format and parsing, the section-slug / bullet-id
allocation scheme, and the helpful/harmful counter semantics in
`src/ace/playbook.py` and `src/ace/merge.py` are derived from that project's
`playbook_utils.py` and `utils.py`. The delta operations (UPDATE / MERGE /
DELETE), the deterministic grow-and-refine, the ACEAdapter/engine architecture,
and the DSPy integration in `src/dspy_ace/` are original to this project.

The method is described in:
    Zhang et al., "Agentic Context Engineering: Evolving Contexts for
    Self-Improving Language Models", arXiv:2510.04618 (ICLR 2026).
